snippet.title: Felvidek Trailer
snippet.description:
Medieval fantasy rpgmaker game set in fictional region of 15th century upper Hungary. See with your own eyes how Ottoman conquest in distant south can affect even our kingdom.

get on steam: 
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2299900/Felvidek/
music done by the amazing @marcelgidotesholycrab 

follow for more info: twitter.com/brozef_
